            "title": "港股跌41點後曾升199點   生科股搶鏡",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒指輕微高開後升幅擴大，最低曾見23503點，跌41點或0.17%，隨後節節向上，約11:13高見23743，升199點或0.85%，為暫時高位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">現報23726，升181點或0.77%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：恒瑞醫藥招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250515_FI_source-web_01726-IPO.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：恒瑞醫藥招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250515_FI_source-web_01726-IPO.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：恒瑞醫藥招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指中升51點或0.97%，報5302點，恒生國企指數升85點或1%，報8643點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市現成交954.88億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥股飆升，首掛恒瑞醫藥(01276)飆31.22%，報57.8元。石藥(01093)升5.56%，報6.84元，為表現最佳藍籌股 ; 藥明康德(02359)升2.76%，報68.59元。信達(01801)升4.21%，報60.4元 ; 三生製藥(01530)升1.1%，報20.2元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">寧德(03750)轉跌，跌2%，報323.3元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">周大福(01929)回落，跌4.36%，報10.96元，為表現最差藍籌股。</p>\n</div>",
